title: A Keynote: Web Summit 2016, Lisbon, Portugal
description: This talk at Web Summit in Lisbon was absolute fire. They put an incredible event on and I just brought it. It's one of the biggest conferences in the world and you know me, I like a crowd :) Take a listen if you haven't seen or heard it yet.
